flowRoot.flowPara: Make the purpose of your work together clear
- “What do you do when working on ... (the subject matter or challenge at hand)? Please make a short list of activities.”
- Keep asking, “Why? Why? Why?” up to nine times or until participants have reached the fundamental purpose for this work
Start with pairs, then groups of four, then the whole group
- Chairs for people to sit face-to-face
